nodes.text: Star Wars: TIE Fighter is a canon comic book miniseries written by Jody Houser and illustrated by Rogê Antônio. The series, which takes place between Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi and Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, focuses on Shadow Wing, a group of elite TIE fighter pilots. The first issue of TIE Fighter was published by Marvel Comics in April 17, 2019.
